				Man you guys must all use your pet REALLY poorly if you think the pet sucks!<BR>
<BR>
This skelly ROCKS!<BR>
You just have to use it correctly.<BR>
<BR>
First of all, make sure the pet ALWAYS fights awa from the creature, because it hits a hech of a lot more when it's slashing into the creature's back instead of front.<BR>
<BR>
 Second of all, if you give the pet a fast, good weapon, it'll hit a lot more and be much more effective.<BR>
<BR>
And lastly, make sure you do engulfing darkness and then fear a lot, and your skelly pet helps a lot also.<BR>
<BR>
But PLEASE, do not use this pet as a tank, and btw, this pet DOES get a random spell proc. In other words, at certain times, it will cast a weak lifetap, well the level 13 pet will at least.<BR>
<BR>
So basically, if used correctly, the pet is effective.<BR>
